Product Requirements Document (PRD)
Product Name: WarkaHub

Meaning: Warka (·ãà·à≠·âÉ) ‚Äì Ficus Vasta tree ‚Üí community, trust, connection
Tagline: Connecting Needs with Trusted Local Services

1. Problem Statement

In Ethiopia:

Catering, event services, transport, labor, cleaning, and rentals are high-demand

Clients struggle to find reliable vendors

Vendors struggle to get consistent, high-paying clients

Middlemen take high commissions without value

No trusted ‚Äúhub‚Äù that works like ride-hailing logic for services

2. Solution Overview (WarkaHub)

WarkaHub is a service-matching hub that connects:

Clients ‚Üí people or businesses who need services

Vendors ‚Üí service providers (catering, event, logistics, labor, etc.)

Using a ride-style matching logic:

Request ‚Üí Match ‚Üí Confirm ‚Üí Deliver ‚Üí Pay

